graph TD
    Start([User clicks<br/>Improve Headings]) --> InitCheck{First<br/>iteration?}
    
    InitCheck -->|Yes| FirstIter[Initialize:<br/>iteration_count = 0<br/>operations = empty<br/>No previous context]
    InitCheck -->|No| ContinueIter[Continue:<br/>Increment iteration_count<br/>Pass previous_iteration_summary<br/>Pass previous_iteration_plan<br/>Include existing_operations]
    
    FirstIter --> CallLLM[Call LLM with:<br/>HTML content<br/>Iteration context<br/>Operation limit = 10<br/>Hierarchical priorities]
    ContinueIter --> CallLLM
    
    CallLLM --> Validate{Validate<br/>operations?}
    
    Validate -->|Invalid| Error[Show error<br/>to user]
    Validate -->|Valid| ApplyOps[Apply operations:<br/>Insert headings<br/>Replace headings<br/>Remove headings]
    
    ApplyOps --> SaveDB[(Save to database:<br/>Operations array<br/>Iteration metadata<br/>Enhancement record)]
    
    SaveDB --> UpdateUI[Update UI:<br/>Show new structure<br/>Display operation count<br/>Show iteration summary]
    
    UpdateUI --> CheckLimits{Safety<br/>limits<br/>reached?}
    
    CheckLimits -->|Yes| ForceStop[Force stop:<br/>Disable buttons<br/>Show limit message<br/>≥5 iterations OR ≥50 ops]
    
    CheckLimits -->|No| CheckMore{LLM says<br/>more_changes_required?}
    
    CheckMore -->|No| Complete[Complete:<br/>Show final structure]
    
    CheckMore -->|Yes| AutoMode{Auto-iterate<br/>enabled?}
    
    AutoMode -->|No| UserChoice[Show buttons:<br/>Continue Improving<br/>Finish]
    AutoMode -->|Yes| AutoContinue[Auto-continue<br/>after 500ms delay]
    
    UserChoice -->|Continue| ContinueIter
    UserChoice -->|Finish| Complete
    AutoContinue --> ContinueIter
    
    Error --> End([End])
    ForceStop --> End
    Complete --> End
    
    style Start fill:#e8f4f8
    style End fill:#e8f4f8
    style CallLLM fill:#fff4e6
    style SaveDB fill:#f0f9ff
    style Error fill:#fee2e2
    style ForceStop fill:#fee2e2
    style Complete fill:#d1fae5